tel_ran.tests.images.tools

Class Tables

  • java.lang.Object
    • tel_ran.tests.images.tools.ImageObject
      • tel_ran.tests.images.tools.Tables

  • public class Tables
extends ImageObject
    Class for ImageObject with a table Table can be with or without borders. It contains two-dimensional array of String or other object and one-dimensional array for headers.

      • Tables

        public Tables(java.lang.String[] header,
              java.lang.String[][] fields,
              Image img,
              java.awt.Font fontHeader,
              java.awt.Font fontFields)
        This constructor uses some parameters of the given image. It may be convinient for most situations, but not flexible
        Parameters:
        header - - String[] array for the table headers. Optional field (can be null)
        fields - - String[][] array for the table text content. Required field for text tables
        img - - link to the given image (class Image) with preset parameters
        fontHeader - - Font for the table Headers. Optional.
        fontFields - - Font for the table content.
